Title: Chocolate crystal skull necklace w moth pendants strega witch dark mori gothic
Description: Extra-long beaded pendant featuring a large Swarovski Crystal skull, in "Antique Gold" (metallic bronze-tinted black). On a hand-wrought bronze chain beaded with smaller chocolate bronze crystals. (Swarovski make Skulls in 2 sizes - This is the large Swarovski skull, not the small one) I chose to make him a long pendant, which can be worn on it's own, or layered with other necklaces. He is satisfyingly heavy, and stays put without being *too* heavy. Perfect, and very tactile (I can't stop playing with mine in the light!). I added a few tiny moth pendants on chains to dangle above the skull. The beaded chain matches his colours - clear AB crystals with a green-ish pink rainbow shimmer. The chain is adjustable, and if preferred longer/shorter just message me the length and I can change it for you. Measurements: skull is 2 cm 2.5 cm high // 3/4 inches to 1 inch Chain is 65 to 77cm (adjustable) // 25 1/2 inches to 30 inches. BLACK, SILVER CHROME, RAINBOW GREEN, and RED skull pendants are also available in my other listings. This item is a handmade creation by Herisson Rose Design, a registered Artisan based in Limousin, France. Different sizing, choice of stones or colours can be requested to order - please allow me a week to make one to your specifications if making a custom order.
